column3: str
This Mol maiden cannot wait to go shopping in Reunion.
Speak with the Mol maiden.
Obtain herbs.
Speak with the Mol maiden.
Obtain shears.
Speak with the Mol maiden.
Obtain seeds.
Deliver the herbs, shears, and seeds to the Mol maiden.
Could I ask you to accompany me while I go shopping?
The udgan told me I am to go shopping with an adventurer today. Meet me in Reunion if you have the time.
Thank you for joining me! I just managed to buy a sack of herbs for a great price.
Though I am not sure if I'm capable of taking them all the way back to Mol Iloh...
Do you think you would be able to carry them for me? I am going to go and look at that stall over there. Thank you!
Oh, I just found the loveliest pair of sheep shears.
Could you manage to carry them as well? I have heard one of the stalls here is going to be running a special sale soon. I need to hurry and find out which!
I am so lucky you are here with me today. I never could have dreamed I would be able to buy so many seeds for such a low price!
Though it seems I sprained my ankle running around searching for the sale just now. Could you be a darling and carry my shopping back home for me? Oh, thank you. You are too kind!
My ankle feels fine now─it is a miracle! Would you happen to have my purchases?
Doubtless it was a heavy load, but I bet it felt like nothing for a strong adventurer such as yourself.
Let me tell you, it was not easy getting my hands on those seeds. They taste incredible when cooked and can also be turned into oil. I had to make full use of my elbows just to avoid missing out.
Of course, it would not have been possible without your help. Here is a reward for all your hard work!
